  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个课堂考勤系统的状态流转图。核心是学生从缺席到签到的流程，还要考虑和LMS门户、成绩同步系统的交互。初始状态应该是ClassroomService触发的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Absent",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我先梳理一下：学生初始是Absent状态，通过扫描\"Start\"可以进入CheckedIn对吗？那如果直接扫\"End\"会怎么样？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "start",
        "end"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，扫\"Start\"进入CheckedIn。但如果学生在Absent时直接扫\"End\"，这是异常操作，要进入Error状态，而且这个动作是由LMS Portal记录的。Error状态需要能重置回Absent。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "Error",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Сброс / Очистка ошибки"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：Absent到CheckedIn是扫\"Start\"，CheckedIn到Attended是扫\"End\"。Error状态我加了个重置路径回Absent。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error",
        "start",
        "end"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，CheckedIn之后如果又扫了\"Start\"呢？有些学生可能会重复扫码。还有Attended之后的状态流转也要考虑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "start",
        "end"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想到两个自循环：CheckedIn时如果扫\"Start\"且来自LMS Portal，就保持CheckedIn；Attended之后无论扫\"Start\"还是\"End\"，只要来自ClassroomService，都保持Attended。这样行吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这样设计合理。另外Error状态需要标注一下原因——这是GradeSync系统识别的无效操作，方便后续排查。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。我在Error右侧加了注释说明是GradeSync检测到的无效操作。整个流程：ClassroomService初始化→Absent，正常扫码完成考勤，异常操作进Error可重置，各系统职责也区分清楚了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
